                                 throws javax.jdo.JDOUserException

        Add category of members.

        If there is a Record And category is FetchGroup.ALL, FetchGroup.BASIC or FetchGroup.DEFAULT Then all the columns of the Record will be immediately added to the members list.

      • removeCategory

        public javax.jdo.FetchGroup removeCategory(String category)
                                    throws javax.jdo.JDOUserException

        Remove members category.

        If category is FetchGroup.ALL Then all members will be cleared. Else if category is FetchGroup.BASIC or FetchGroup.DEFAULT Then all columns of the Record will be removed from members.
        Specified by:
